  <title>Authentication Policies</title>
  <para>
    Authentication Policy defines the type of verification that must be performed to provide a sufficient level of trust for Access Manager to grant access to the user making the request.
    A single policy can be defined to protect one or more resources in the Application Domain.
  </para>
